Params: {2: 'Chrome', 3: "I've picked out all the largest women's clothing... Now we just have to wait for Murray to contact us.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "Which reminds me, I'm surprised you were able to keep your curiosity at bay and refrain from asking Murray about Lee. Almost thought you were an imposter.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "I'm real curious, but I still have some common sense. I know what to ask and what not to.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'After all, that Murray... is probably what spurs Lee on.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'If only you were normally this smart. Come to think of it, so what spurs you on? When Wanshi and the others asked you about it last time, you kept stuttering.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "I'll keep stuttering, then. After all, that fella's the one who has the say when it comes to this topic.", 4: '2'}
{3: 'When Chrome mentions Camu, Kamui gestures at him to shush.'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Anyway, there's no point in sitting here waiting. How about I try it on for size first?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "It's... probably not as hard as we think it is. I've seen similar clothes. Sit down first, Kamui.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "Don't move. First, let's fit your head through this hole in the dress..."}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Wait a sec, Captain! My Inver-Device is stuck!'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: '...Just hold your head up and arch your back a bit. And now let me pull the back zipper up.'}
{2: 'Chrome', 3: "It's already the biggest one we can find. Try to keep it down."}
{3: 'When Murray finally returns, what greets him is a messy heap made of clothes and two Strike Hawk members.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Changing into clothes... is a different beast than combat.', 4: '2'}
{3: 'Judging from the traumatic situation, the two must have battled with a Leviathan. Murray thinks so while sending the materials he prepared to Chrome.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Murray', 3: "Anyway, I'll handle the rest. Can we dress Kamui again and put makeup on him under my orders?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Murray', 3: "It's too late to say that now, Kamui...", 4: '1'}
